{"tid":2156162,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【荃灣中槍學生不獲批法援！署方：警方武力合理】","createTime":"2020-08-14T09:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:55:38.000Z","uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa7c1acb47720df91f16bcdfceb258786b0e518","tid":2156162,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"【荃灣中槍學生不獲批法援！署方：警方武力合理】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRCMfA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRCMfA1.jpg&h=d32e1273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年十月一日，荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學的曾同學被黑警近距離以實彈射穿左胸。當時，子彈碎片分布肋骨、肺及胸腔，與心臟只有三厘米距離，事件引來極大公憤。<br />\n<br />\n曾同學早前就此入稟人身傷害索償，怎料卻收到法援署來信，表明拒絕法援申請，署方竟離譜得白紙黑字表明「本署認為警方於相關時間向你所使用的武力是合理的」。<br />\n<br />\n坦白說，法援署的近月不斷收緊審坦批準則，本來經已為人詬病，政治審查越加明顯，處處留難手足，亦已非新鮮事物。不過，我真的未曾料到署方如今會變本加厲，瘋狂至如此地步。<br />\n<br />\n本來入稟索償的重點，就是爭論警方武力是否合理，如今法援署竟擔當判官角色，未審訊、未開庭、未盤問，已直接代法庭裁定「警方使用武力合理」，實在讓人歎為觀止。<br />\n<br />\n據悉曾同學將會上訴，目前未知上訴排期早子為何，但這也提醒我們，政權無所不用其極的滲透與打壓，達到怎麼過份的程度，相信只會導致國際對香港司法體系運作再度投下不信任票。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3237065166385969/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F3237065166385969%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=e1ea6cac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3237065166385969/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"872b9b56846664cdd43c41cd66a27b5fa090b911","tid":2156162,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca2cfa81d16b2eb86d5748b4f3d23b25b3443bd","tid":2156162,"uid":282011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a640e60fef9efb7386796555aee606c44c86a3","tid":2156162,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"wtf"},{"pid":"44e865a6b8805d6f1aee94fbad4c8f6c42c0b879","tid":2156162,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"Dllm無恥至極"},{"pid":"bbc9d945f27d4477e21e9a0aeab958fe7bea63df","tid":2156162,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03d2548859d6cd69998f4f000a5ffe2c3a9527","tid":2156162,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b338d18c7febbfbce36767adcab18c2241bfd8ed","tid":2156162,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b8f1934c70b451f69cd1932712b4de62867d3ce","tid":2156162,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}